      <title>葡萄牙仍未决定出售其在 TAP 的股份规模</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/portugal-still-to-decide-on-size-of-stake-it-will-sell-in-tap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙财政部长若阿金·米兰达·萨尔门托 (Joaquim Miranda Sarmento) 表示，葡萄牙政府仍未决定在国有航空公司私有化计划中出售多少葡萄牙航空股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/portugal-still-to-decide-on-size-of-stake-it-will-sell-in-tap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 14:51:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
