    <item>
      <title>哈维称股市将突破“忧虑之墙”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-09/stocks-will-scale-this-wall-of-worry-harvey-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富国银行股票策略主管克里斯·哈维表示，随着美联储缓慢降息，明年股市和风险都将走高。他正在接受“彭博监测”采访。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-09/stocks-will-scale-this-wall-of-worry-harvey-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 14:36:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Apollo 旗下 Novolex 将收购包装竞争对手 Pactiv Evergreen</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/novolex-to-pay-18-a-share-for-packaging-rival-pactive-evergreen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 旗下的包装公司 Novolex 表示，将以每股 18 美元（包括债务）的价格收购竞争对手 Pactiv Evergreen Inc.，总价为 67 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/novolex-to-pay-18-a-share-for-packaging-rival-pactive-evergreen</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 13:16:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>融资受到审查，MicroStrategy 购买更多比特币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/microstrategy-buys-more-bitcoin-as-funding-draws-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[MicroStrategy Inc. 又购买了价值 21 亿美元的比特币，而其通过出售股票和固定收益证券为快速增加的收购提供资金的做法也受到了越来越多的审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/microstrategy-buys-more-bitcoin-as-funding-draws-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 13:14:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新日铁为赢得美国工人支持做最后努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/nippon-steel-clarifies-spending-pledge-in-effort-to-save-us-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新日本制铁公司公布了其在美国钢铁公司旗下美国钢厂的支出计划，这是其为争取工人和政界人士支持收购这家匹兹堡钢铁制造商而做出的最后一项努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/nippon-steel-clarifies-spending-pledge-in-effort-to-save-us-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 13:03:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国巴黎银行第二次增加 SRT 以支持 170 亿欧元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/bnp-boosts-srt-for-a-second-time-to-back-17-billion-of-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，法国巴黎银行第二次增加了与重大风险转移相关的企业贷款组合规模，这是投资者对此类交易的需求不断增长的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/bnp-boosts-srt-for-a-second-time-to-back-17-billion-of-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 12:33:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：CPI 公布前几天股市涨势减弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/asian-markets-cautious-amid-geopolitical-tensions-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在经历了强劲上涨之后，股市有望创下 2019 年以来的最佳年度表现，但随后却难以取得进展，交易员们正在等待有助于影响美联储利率前景的关键通胀数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/asian-markets-cautious-amid-geopolitical-tensions-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 22:41:08 GMT</pubDate>
